      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KIANDO PIPER (2) goes very well at this journey here having never missed the frame including three wins and two placings. Scored by a nose last time (20.02) in a Grade 5 over 340m at this track. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. KARINYA TOM TOM (4) has been out of the placings the last couple but was a Grade 5 winner (19.71) three back at this track. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. MOTOR CITY BOMB (1) has some solid form under her belt and proved too classy last time to win by 1.3 lengths at this track in a handy 20.06 beating Sketchy Sister. Looks a key chance if runs up to latest figure. TRAIN OF THOUGHT (6) scored by a nose last time (19.75) in a Grade 5 over 340m at this track. Unbeaten in two runs from this draw.",
